Package: blackjack-pro
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.7), python3-tk
Description: Professional Blackjack card counting training simulator
 Blackjack Pro is a comprehensive desktop application for learning and
 practicing Blackjack with integrated card counting simulation.
 .
 Features:
  * Multiple card counting systems (Hi-Lo, KO, Omega II)
  * Deviation indices (Illustrious 18 + Fab Four)
  * Real-time basic strategy recommendations
  * Save/Load game sessions
  * CSV statistics export
  * Professional training features
 .
 Perfect for learning optimal Blackjack strategy and card counting
 techniques in a safe, educational environment.
